cs.CL, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and its application to code summarization and generation tasks. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on automatic software development tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach to solve the dual tasks of code summarization and generation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach to improve the performance of two important AI tasks. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on programming language design or implementation, but rather on the application of NLP and machine learning to software development tasks.
